00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:31.480
The memorial

00:02:32.320 --> 00:02:34.280
Please deliver it for me, Eunuch

00:03:00.200 --> 00:03:00.920
Your Majesty

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:02.240
Lord Rui

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:04.920
