Concern clouds judgment

00:03:32.760 --> 00:03:34.920
Generals committing crimes is a grave matter

00:03:35.440 --> 00:03:36.240
I wonder

00:03:36.880 --> 00:03:38.640
what the two chief judges of this case

00:03:39.200 --> 00:03:40.200
think about it

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:41.600
I

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:43.840
will thoroughly investigate both cases

00:03:43.960 --> 00:03:45.200
and allow no mistakes

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:48.880
I believe

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:51.320
we should choose someone for this case

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:53.800
who has no connections at all

